Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.84,0:23:38.16,TEXT-CN UP,,0,0,0,,又做了什么坏事了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:23:38.16,0:23:40.02,TEXT-CN UP,,0,0,0,,镜 镜 镜
